 example
  :START COUNT=0
   TY Enter the number of times you want to repeat the statement:
   ACCEPT
   MAX=NUMBER.(1)
   :LOOP
   TY This loop has run #COUNT times it will terminate when it runs #MAX times
   IF COUNT<MAX,
      COUNT=COUNT+1
      GO TO :LOOP
   TY Do you want to do this again?
   ACCEPT
   IF 'yes', GO TO START
   IF 'no' GO TO FINISH
   :FINISH
   TY Goodbye!
   STOP
